Interface UnboundSafeUpdaterBuilder<S,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The type of value understood by the topic
    T - The type of value updates are provided as

extends SafeUpdaterBuilder<S,T>, UnboundUpdaterBuilder<S,T,SafeTransformedUpdater<S,T>,SafeTransformedUpdateSource<S,T>>
